  "body": "## Description\n\nThis PR deduplicates and aligns Metro configuration handling in `@module-federation/metro`, including typing/default behavior cleanup across plugin paths.\n\nChanges include:\n- align metro-core config typings and defaults used by plugin paths\n- centralize option normalization/validation and warning handling\n- migrate plugin specs to Vitest + memfs\n- update Metro plugin docs\n\n## Related Issue\n\nN/A\n\n## Types of changes\n\n- [x] Docs change / refactoring / dependency upgrade\n- [x] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)\n- [ ] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)\n\n## Checklist\n\n- [x] I have added tests to cover my changes.\n- [ ] All new and existing tests passed.\n- [x] I have updated the documentation.\n",
